+# Copilot advisory v2 operator/laboratory projection
+
+```text
+validated intake
+      |
+      v
+source advisory schema dispatch
+  |                         |
+  v                         v
+v1 projection            v2 first-opinion projection
+(summary/route/...)       (objective/result/constraints/criteria)
+  |                         |
+  +------------+------------+
+               v
+existing hint-only context-ref injection
+               v
+existing operator-approved fake-laboratory command
+               v
+existing Scheduler
+               v
+version-matched local publication preview
+```
+
+The two analytical contracts stay separate. Only technical provenance,
+authority flags and the context-reference mechanism are shared.
